==機內服務==
芒果航空有一個上機前購買計畫，提供[[飲品|飲品]]和[[食物|食物]]。<ref>"[http://ww5.flymango.com/UserRsx/images/SpazaMango1.jpg Spaza Mango 1] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090227200512/http://ww5.flymango.com/UserRsx/images/SpazaMango1.jpg |date=2009-02-27 }}." ''芒果航空''. 訪問在二零零八年十月三十號。</ref><ref>"[http://ww5.flymango.com/UserRsx/images/SpazaMango2.jpg Spaza Mango 2] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090227200521/http://ww5.flymango.com/UserRsx/images/SpazaMango2.jpg |date=2009-02-27 }}." ''芒果航空''. 訪問在二零零八年十月三十號。</ref>

